{"tid":1472861,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"無論係國泰定tvb疑似跪低呢件事，都證明左任何大機構只睇一樣野","createTime":"2019-08-14T16:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T17:30:50.000Z","uid":81236,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc72234c5162ada119aa45162c23b01eb38f6e0","tid":1472861,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:39:25.000Z","msg":"就係錢<br />\n<br />\n但我地香港人就係要話比全世界知<br />\n<br />\n我地要既自由、民主、良知<br />\n唔係可以用錢去衡量<br />\n<br />\n錢可以收買任何一個機構<br />\n可以收買任何一個人<br />\n<br />\n有人話我地要玉石俱焚，將香港推落深淵<br />\n<br />\n你可以用經濟恐嚇我<br />\n你可以用強權打壓我<br />\n但你永遠埋沒我心中既良知<br />\n<br />\n你地當權者永遠都沒法明白運動既動力<br />\n唔係金錢，唔係權力，唔係名利<br />\n<br />\n而係留係香港人對民主自由既追求，刻係香港人心中既良知。"},{"pid":"070abdf5d819dab493982e13babdb28a1497a9d4","tid":1472861,"uid":164730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"tvb唔同，佢跟本比中資控制"},{"pid":"031177e7a968795fcd00671dec7e948d30a9a4e1","tid":1472861,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"070abdf5d819dab493982e13babdb28a1497a9d4","tid":1472861,"uid":164730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"tvb唔同，佢跟本比中資控制"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:41:59.000Z","msg":"任何機構都係對股東交代<br />\n<br />\n但我地既運動係呢一代，下一代，同埋以後既每一代交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5168171c404e42a918a8b976f8feb8a126512e6b","tid":1472861,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:49:33.000Z","msg":"唔好意思各位，借個位宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">818百萬人大遊行<br />\n黑警還眼<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家開始全民投入宣傳工作<br />\n<strong><span style